Download and install the uBlock extension from here https://ublockorigin.com .
Click on the uBlock extension, then click “Settings” in the bottom-right corner.
Copy and paste the following code into uBlock’s “My Filters”:



! ====== BLOCK SHORTS COMPLETELY ======
www.youtube.com##a[href^="/shorts"]
www.youtube.com##ytd-reel-shelf-renderer
www.youtube.com##ytd-reel-item-renderer
www.youtube.com##ytd-rich-shelf-renderer:has-text(/Shorts/i)
www.youtube.com##[aria-label="Shorts"]
www.youtube.com##ytd-mini-guide-entry-renderer:has(a[href^="/shorts"])

! ====== HIDE UP NEXT & END SCREEN ======
www.youtube.com##.ytp-endscreen-content
www.youtube.com##.ytp-upnext
www.youtube.com##.ytp-ce-element
www.youtube.com##.ytp-ce-covering-overlay

! ====== REMOVE RIGHT SIDEBAR (RECOMMENDED) ======
www.youtube.com###related

! Optional: widen player
www.youtube.com#$#body#body { margin: 0 !important; } 
www.youtube.com#$#.ytd-watch-flexy[flexy][is-two-columns_]:not([fullscreen]) #primary.ytd-watch-flexy { width: calc(100% - 40px) !important; }
